      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STILTON SUPREME (2) is a first starter from the Peter Lagogiane yard by Equalizer out of Opulence. Gets every chance from the inside draw. Respect any strong moves in the market. TOM TRICKERY (1) showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 7th at this track in Maiden company. Comes out of a solid form race last start. A big run wouldn't surprise. GO FORWARD BOBBY (8) profiles well for this but has a wide draw to content with at his first outing. Bold showing expected here. HARD SNIFF STYLE (7) was well supported last time but could only manage third (18.73), beaten 2.25 lengths. Form from his last run is proving strong. Well placed and gets his chance.",
